I know I did this already but I wanted to do that part. 

The thing is you can't beat your audience over the head with everything. Use some subtext, make the reader think and engage with the text a little. 

'How could Ventress and Anakin share the same fate? Maybe if Maul...'

Obi-Wan: Anakin, her fate could have easily been yours.

Anakin stops and takes a deep breath.

Anakin: She needs medical attention...

Obi Wan: Ventress! 

Obi-Wan goes to help Ventress. Anakin rushes ahead but stops and looks back noticing Obi Wan isn't following

Anakin: Leave Her!

Obi Wan checks Ventress' pulse
